#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This add-on is designed to temporarily kill NVDA, so that you can recover if "
"it freezes."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj je dodatak osmišljen za privremeno prisilno zatvaranje NVDA čitača, "
"kako bi se obnovio, ako zastane."

#. type: Title ##
#, no-wrap
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Primjena"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Install this add-on."
msgstr "Instaliraj ovaj dodatak."

#. type: Bullet: '2. '
msgid "Copy it to the logon screen with the button in General Settings."
msgstr "Kopiraj ga na prozor prijave s gumbom u općim postavkama."

#. type: Bullet: '3. '
msgid ""
"When NVDA dies, press control alt delete, then activate the NVDA menu, "
"Tools, Kill NVDA."
msgstr ""
"Kad NVDA zastane, pritisni kontrol alt dilit. Zatim aktiviraj NVDA izbornik, "
"Alati, Prisilno zatvori NVDA."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"After that, press escape. NVDA restarts, but you should be able to use your "
"computer again."
msgstr ""
"Nakon toga pritisni eskeip. NVDA se ponovo pokreće, ali bi se računalo "
"moralo moći ponovo koristiti."

